Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The property is located in the consistently strong Desoto County submarket of Memphis, which has been a hotbed of new industrial development. The attractiveness of city and state incentives as well as ample land has brought many developers and users to this area. While inventory continues to increase, it is still not outpacing the demand in the area allowing for some of the highest industrial rents and sale prices in our entire market. The Desoto Co. submarket currently has a vacancy rate of 8.6% on 53,000,000 SF of product

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present the property at 10630 Marina Dr. Olive Branch, MS for lease. The property is located in the Desoto Co. Submarket of the Memphis, TN MSA and includes 121,300 SF Warehouse with 6,300 SF Office, total of 127,600 SF on 9.16 Acres. The property was developed in 1994 and renovated in early 2020. The building has been used as a manufacturing and assembly plant and has a large amount of power. In addition, the property is situated within an established, well located industrial park with easy access to the Olive Branch Airport as well as the main arteries of Hwy 302, I-269, and I-22.

This building has unique features such as multiple cranes and heavy power that make it standout from more standard distribution buildings of like size. The building has an attractive façade and a fully fenced loading and outside storage area for a multitude of uses. Also, there is ample parking for any future manufacturer or user with 118 parking spaces. 10630 Marina Dr. is an excellent option for any manufacturer or distribution user who is looking to lease or buy one of the few concrete-tilt buildings available in the Desoto Co. submarket.
